  "detailed_description": "Taken Away is a non-linear strategic horror game. Following a car \"accident\", you have been abducted. Explore your surroundings, don't get caught, figure out a way to escape... or face a gruesome death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/c08e462715509aab948a54391d53520f.avif?t=1738927295\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br>Every game is unique, each run starts with a random setup: items placement changes, passwords are randomly generated. The Dog and the Man's behaviors can be unpredictable, and should be handled with care.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/8808e7133b3e66bb4848da624f9c04fb.avif?t=1738927295\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br>You will face many hurdles and challenges, making it alive will be tough...<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Searching the house is the #1 key to your success, but the Man doesn't really like it...<br></li><li>His pet Wolf doesn't like you either, stay low.<br></li><li>Avoid traps, pick locks, listen carefully to all sound cues and be smarter than the enemy!<br></li><li>Play a video game inside the game!<br></li><li>Grab some vegetables, and make soup! Might be useful, who knows...<br></li><li>What is this strange growl coming from the basement?</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=512 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=502 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=512 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Taken Away is a non-linear strategic horror game. Following a car \"accident\", you have been abducted. Explore your surroundings, don't get caught, figure out a way to escape... or face a gruesome death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/c08e462715509aab948a54391d53520f.avif?t=1738927295\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br>Every game is unique, each run starts with a random setup: items placement changes, passwords are randomly generated. The Dog and the Man's behaviors can be unpredictable, and should be handled with care.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/8808e7133b3e66bb4848da624f9c04fb.avif?t=1738927295\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br>You will face many hurdles and challenges, making it alive will be tough...<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Searching the house is the #1 key to your success, but the Man doesn't really like it...<br></li><li>His pet Wolf doesn't like you either, stay low.<br></li><li>Avoid traps, pick locks, listen carefully to all sound cues and be smarter than the enemy!<br></li><li>Play a video game inside the game!<br></li><li>Grab some vegetables, and make soup! Might be useful, who knows...<br></li><li>What is this strange growl coming from the basement?</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=512 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/0e5b7c999194a8e7549f3024391d226a.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=502 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/87ef3b15ffb5930474a9bf2d07d18529.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.poster.avif?t=1738927295\" width=512 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.webm?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1322090/extras/cb9728aba4b4d011d29b0e57e0f03e85.mp4?t=1738927295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
